Name: Average resolution time difference between 'Completed + Cancelled' and 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + Cancelled' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Median duration from 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Longest duration from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Shortest duration from any activity to 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average duration from 'Completed + Cancelled' to the next activity in the process
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Completed + Cancelled and the end of the case

Name: Total duration of all 'Completed + Cancelled' activities in the event log
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Completed + Cancelled and the end of the case

Name: Duration variance of 'Completed + Cancelled' compared to 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + Cancelled' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Earliest occurrence time of 'Completed + Cancelled' after 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Latest occurrence time of 'Completed + Cancelled' before 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Completed + Cancelled' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average duration between 'Completed + Cancelled' and 'Accepted + Assigned' in the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + Cancelled' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Total elapsed time involving 'Completed + Cancelled' in the top 5 longest process variants
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Completed + Cancelled and the end of the case

Name: Minimum duration of 'Completed + Cancelled' activities in cases involving 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Completed + Cancelled and the end of the case

Name: Maximum duration of 'Completed + Cancelled' activities in cases involving 'Accepted + Wait - Customer'
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Completed + Cancelled' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x00000221C2305210> - AppliesTo.PROCESS filtered by the function ma > 0 where ma is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + Wait - Customer'
